📖 **Tashrih:**
    Dastoor `l2test` baraye test kardan etesalate layer 2 (data link layer) dar shabake estefade mishavad.  In dastoor oboore packet-ha ra az tarighe yek shabake azmaysh mikonad. Agar `l2test` mojood nabashad, ehtemalan bayad az narm afzar-haye digari mesle `ping` ya `traceroute` baraye test etesalat shabake estefade konid.  

⚙️ **Gozine-ha:**
    Az aanja ke `l2test` yek dastoor standard nist, gozine-ha va amalkarde aan momken ast motefavet bashad ya voojood nadashte bashad. Agar dastoor dar system-e shoma mojood bashad, az `man l2test` ya `l2test --help` baraye didane gozine-haye momken estefade konid.

🛠 **Mesal-ha:**
    Az aanja ke `l2test` yek dastoor standard nist, mesal-haye khassi nemitoonim benevisim. Dar soorate dashtane in dastoor, dastoorat mesale `l2test -h` baraye rahnamayi estefade konid. Be tor mamool, agar chonin dastoor vojood dashte bashad, momken ast shekle zir dashte bashad:

    $ l2test -i eth0 -c 10 192.168.1.1
    🔹 Test etesale layer 2 az interface eth0 ba ersale 10 packet be address 192.168.1.1

✅ **Mesal sade:**
    Az aanja ke `l2test` yek dastoor mamool nist, yek mesal sade baraye namayesh voojood nadarad. Behtar ast az dastoor haye dige baraye test shabake estefade konid.

